title: 'I'm A Celebrity' 2015: Stephanie Davis Joins Line-Up Following 'Hollyoaks' Axe?
text:
'I'm A Celebrity' 2015: Stephanie Davis Joins Line-Up Following 'Hollyoaks' Axe? The Huffington Post UK | By Daniel Welsh 
However, ITV bosses look to have thrown Stephanie a lifeline, with reports suggesting she’ll be among the famous line-up heading Down Under next month. 
Stephanie Davis 
An insider told The Mirror: “Stephanie is hot property and the reality shows have all been desperate to sign her up since her sacking as they know she is mouthy and prone to crazy antics. 
“However, Steph is also keen to prove herself and wants viewers to see her stronger side taking part in jungle challenges and interacting with the other contestants. 
“She knows ‘I’m A Celeb’ won’t be easy, but thinks the experience will be positive overall.” 
Of course, while she’s best known for her antics both on and off screen with ‘Hollyoaks’, some may remember that Stephanie is no stranger to reality television, first getting her big break on the BBC series ‘Over The Rainbow’.
